  "author": "XO_OX Designs",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "S-curve arc, 30 seconds, peak 1.0. The definitive long-form Conductor preset. Begins in near-silence with high breath and low effort. Over half a minute the entire engine transforms: vowel morphs from U to A, effort builds from whisper to full belt, filter opens, partials lock into total synchrony. Then it releases. The final curtain call — one held chord becomes a complete performance that ends in silence.",
